PatternDescription: Third-party library present in application lib folder (exploded project).
Fix: OC4J is obsolete; move runtime to a supported javax.* container (e.g., Tomcat 9) to keep dual-runtime compatibility.
RemediationDescription: Remove OC4J-specific libs and migrate deployment; validate on JDK 8 and JDK 21.

PatternDescription: Third-party library present in application lib folder (exploded project).
Fix: Struts 1.x is obsolete; dual-runtime goal requires migrating away from Struts 1 (e.g., Spring MVC on javax.* container) or another maintained framework.
RemediationDescription: Framework migration required; large code/config changes; regression testing on both runtimes.
